<reference id="vrmlist" xml:lang="en-us">
   <title>
      <keyword>vrmlist</keyword>
   </title>
   <shortdesc>The &lt;<keyword>vrmlist</keyword>&gt; element contains
a set of &lt;<keyword>vrm</keyword>&gt; elements for logging the version, release,
and modification information for multiple products or versions of products
to which the topic applies.</shortdesc>
   <prolog>
      <metadata>
         <keywords>
            <indexterm>vrmlist</indexterm>
            <indexterm>Prolog
elements<indexterm>vrmlist</indexterm>
            </indexterm>
            <indexterm>vrmlist</indexterm>
         </keywords>
      </metadata>
   </prolog>
   <refbody>
      <refsyn>
         <title>Contained by</title>
         <xref href="prodinfo.xml">prodinfo</xref>
      </refsyn>
      <refsyn>
         <title>Contains</title>
         <xref href="vrm.xml">vrm</xref>
      </refsyn>
      <section>
         <title>Attributes</title>
         <simpletable relcolwidth="2* 3* 1* 1* 1*" id="vrmlist_attr">
            <sthead>
               <stentry>Name</stentry>
               <stentry>Description</stentry>
               <stentry>Data Type</stentry>
               <stentry>Default Value</stentry>
               <stentry>Required?</stentry>
            </sthead>
            <strow conref="commonLRdefs.xml#commonLRdefs/global-atts">
               <stentry/>
               <stentry/>
               <stentry/>
               <stentry/>
               <stentry/>
            </strow>
            <strow conref="commonLRdefs.xml#commonLRdefs/class">
               <stentry/>
               <stentry/>
               <stentry/>
               <stentry/>
               <stentry/>
            </strow>
         </simpletable>
      </section>
      <example>
         <p>The recent versions of a mythical product might be logged thus
using the vrmlist markup:</p>
         <codeblock>&lt;prolog&gt;
 &lt;metadata&gt;
  &lt;prodinfo&gt;
   &lt;prodname&gt;Widge-o-matic&lt;/prodname&gt;
   &lt;vrmlist&gt;
     &lt;vrm version="1.0" release="2001-03-30" modification="0"/&gt;
     &lt;vrm version="1.0" modification="1" release="2001-10-03"/&gt;
   &lt;/vrmlist&gt;
  &lt;/prodinfo&gt;
 &lt;/metadata&gt;
&lt;/prolog&gt;
</codeblock>
      </example>
   </refbody>
